des: Catch up with the messages from the Evangel Wichita preaching team. You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day. You can also ask for previous and next episodes by saying "Alexa, previous" and "Alexa, next".
